    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1891-12-05T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1891-12-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="272"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d272">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Smith</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Blaine</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Hawaiian Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington, D. C.</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-12-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 5, 1891</hi>
                        </date>. (Received December 8.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I am instructed to convey to you the recognition
                    and high appreciation of Her Majesty the Queen, and of her Government, of the
                    official courtesies tendered on the occasion of the obsequies of Hon. H. A. P.
                    Carter, Her Majesty’s late minister plenipotentiary and envoy extraordinary.</p>
                <p>Permit me, Mr. Secretary, to add my personal appreciation also of the official
                    respect shown to the memory of my late distinguished friend.</p>
                <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">J. Mott Smith</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
